WEBVTT

0
00:00:00.009 --> 00:00:03.670
To add or remove columns in a list in Service Operations Workspace,

1
00:00:03.910 --> 00:00:06.969
open the List Actions menu using the gear icon,

2
00:00:07.210 --> 00:00:08.710
then select "Edit columns".

3
00:00:09.439 --> 00:00:13.319
The Edit List window shows the columns currently displayed on the right

4
00:00:13.479 --> 00:00:15.699
and all available columns on the left.

5
00:00:16.940 --> 00:00:18.010
To add a column,

6
00:00:18.229 --> 00:00:20.270
scroll or search for the field you need,

7
00:00:20.549 --> 00:00:23.069
then select it from the "Available columns" list.

8
00:00:25.780 --> 00:00:27.069
To remove a column,

9
00:00:27.340 --> 00:00:29.409
find it in the "Selected columns" panel,

10
00:00:29.829 --> 00:00:31.389
then click the remove icon.

11
00:00:32.168 --> 00:00:32.979
When you're finished,

12
00:00:33.130 --> 00:00:36.659
click "OK" to apply your changes and return to the list.

13
00:00:37.599 --> 00:00:38.439
As you can see,

14
00:00:38.520 --> 00:00:41.000
the removed column is no longer displayed,

15
00:00:41.279 --> 00:00:43.700
and the added column now appears in the list.

16
00:00:43.930 --> 00:00:46.380
These changes apply only to your personal view

17
00:00:46.569 --> 00:00:48.340
and won't affect what others see.
